---
title: Samosa-Inspired Bison Meat Pies with Mango Chutney Sauce
description: Hand pies are not traditionally the quickest thing to make, but one bite into that flaky crust and savoury meat-filled center will make it all worth it! The sweet and tangy mango chutney sauce is the perfect dipping companion!
